---
By: Ramakrishna
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 194
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - God's Will
---
Live in the world like a dead leaf. As a dead leaf is carried by the wind
into a house or on the roadside and has no choice of its own, so let the
wind of the Divine Will blow you wherever it chooses.
